{"tid":52342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優帶少女開雜交趴被捕　素顏照曝光","createTime":"2016-12-24T03:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T13:51:35.000Z","uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e26ac5c66b75c589da293aa513049d18c958dbb0","tid":52342,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:58:22.000Z","msg":"美國21歲AV女優賓德羅絲(Bianca Byndloss)，因涉嫌帶3名未成年少女開雜交趴，而遭到逮捕，她的清純素顏照也跟著曝光。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，案情指出，賓德羅絲被控在前年帶著3名分別為12、13、14歲的少女，與2名18歲男子，一起開雜交趴。賓德羅絲也讓少女們喝伏特加、嗑藥阿普唑侖(Xanax)。據少女們說法，現場就是「大家做愛來做愛去，射來射去」，還用手機拍下雜交過程。賓德羅絲被逮後，遭控猥褻兒童、對兒童進行性行為等罪。<br />\n <br />\n該案在本月初進行宣判，賓德羅絲雖然不用被關，但要繳交罰金754美元(約新台幣23000元)以及緩刑10年。涉案的2名男子在今年稍早，也已被判緩刑10年。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161224/1019807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20161224%2F1019807&d=S5hC4lpB7aC5S1kjtA%2FrcnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a69f8a8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161224/1019807</a>"},{"pid":"54ca44734301a870e8b84253b5777007464419b4","tid":52342,"uid":4329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:00:50.000Z","msg":"差咁啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5717fa3048070a179ea0724e85d86fe1ae9a23d2","tid":52342,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:03:41.000Z","msg":"Seed or mother"},{"pid":"2cb0b1a753cf5062755c625a7b93e15a552b6495","tid":52342,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/713JyTC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F713JyTC.jpg&h=94eab0bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主老母saved"},{"pid":"8b615d2a409106b7cdcd576761dbd8a68b460391","tid":52342,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-